name: epl::page
body:
A place to put related files to UT EE380L Engineering Programming Language course. 

Subdirectories

- [note](note): classnotes in markdown format
- [project\_doc](project_doc): where I keep the documentations for projects in .md and generated html format. Currently documentation is generated with [cldoc](https://github.com/jessevdk/cldoc) tool.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
